{"tid":2352431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★突發！SONY互動娛樂亞洲中心營運部從香港移到新加坡","createTime":"2021-01-04T04:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T05:14:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d9eaa08ff6d7e1c3fa2769c09d8aeb71d30ac17e","tid":2352431,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:37:18.000Z","msg":"索尼互動娛樂亞洲市場 (SIE Asia)主管香港、台灣、韓國、新加坡、馬來西亞、菲律賓等地區的業務，其亞洲中心營運部一直也在香港作據點，而近日正式將營運部從香港移到新加坡。索尼互動娛樂亞洲事業營運部主管村瀨勝彥將會帶領後續發展，香港董事總經理 Mustafa Yiğit，以及曾任索尼互動娛樂香港總經理與亞洲市場傳播總監的 Jacqueline Chiu 也轉到新加坡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2021/01/02/sie-asia-move-from-hk-to-singapore/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2021%2F01%2F02%2Fsie-asia-move-from-hk-to-singapore%2F&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZycpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=b410b6be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2021/01/02/sie-asia-move-from-hk-to-singapore/</a>"},{"pid":"5d72dba27e883b7a3f09e4672024d79c90388079","tid":2352431,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ab99168f5a583151a9d987893ce92829feb704","tid":2352431,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:38:07.000Z","msg":"買ps5 只可玩 北韓賽車 不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces